org.xmlcml.euclid
Class Real2Range

java.lang.Object
  org.xmlcml.euclid.Real2Range

public class Real2Range
extends java.lang.Object

2-D double limits Contains two RealRanges. Can therefore be used to describe 2-dimensional limits (for example axes of graphs, rectangles in graphics, limits of a molecule, etc.)

Default is two default/invalid RealRange components. Adding points will create valid ranges.

Author:
(C) P. Murray-Rust, 1996
